    Page: 262 f
By: Ananda Moyi Ma
---
Many Feel the urge to create a new and better world. Rather than let your
thoughts dwell on such matters, you should concentrate on That by the
contemplation of which there is hope of perfect peace. It is man's duty
to become a seeker after God or Truth.
